data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Red Rock Valley Estates, nestled in the picturesque landscapes of Colorado Springs. This exquisite single-family residence boasts an array of features that truly make it a one-of-a-kind retreat. The heart of the home features a gourmet kitchen adorned with sleek stainless steel appliances. Imagine waking up to the awe-inspiring sight of majestic mountains right outside your window while a fire crackles in the wood-burning stove. The terra cotta tiles on the roof not only add to the architectural beauty but also infuse a touch of rustic charm. Natural light floods the sunroom, adorned with beamed wood ceilings, and offers a seamless view of the beauty outside through floor-to-ceiling windows. The current craft room can easily be converted to an additional bedroom or reverted back to garage space since floating walls were utilized in its construction. Step outside to the fenced backyard, a haven for outdoor enthusiasts and gardeners alike. Whether you desire to utilize the wood deck behind the house or the covered patio in front, this home's location offers breathtaking 360-degree views from any spot on the property. A few of the additional standout features of this property are the new windows, passive solar, 50 amp service tailored for your RV, additional shed and barn, and a hydrant to complement the fire-mitigated property. With over 2 acres of land at your disposal, the possibilities are endless. In the coveted Red Rock Valley Estates, you'll find a harmonious blend of community and privacy. Enjoy the tranquility of the countryside while being within easy reach of Colorado Springs' amenities and attractions. Whether it's the nearby parks, schools, or vibrant city life, you're always just a stone's throw away from everything you need. Don't miss your chance to make this captivating home your very own. Schedule a viewing today and let the mountains become your new neighbors.
